Section Manager Used Car Sales - PT Mercedes-Benz Indonesia
Section Manager Used Car Sales  -
Section Manager Used Car Sales
Responsibilities
Job Responsibilities: To develop and implement a suitable business model of used car business and to integrate with the new car sales.To liaise with relevant business partner and orchestrate sales activities to deliver positive business result.To secure the high level of Mercedes-Benz cars' residual value and extend Mercedes-Benz customer base. Qualification/Requirements:Education: Minimum of Bachelor degree in Management, Economic or equivalent. Experience: Minimum 3 years’ experience in Retail Sales or Marketing.Strong network for Used Car Market or Independent Used Car Showroom and Traders. Specific Knowledge and Skills: Comprehensive knowledge in sales process.Good English and Indonesian correspondence skills both written and spoken.Computer literate; MS Office (Word, Excel, and PowerPoint); and advance skills of MS Excel.Good presentation and negotiation skills.Possess Salesmanship and good communication skills.
